---
// Features Grid Section
// 6 feature cards showcasing key app capabilities
---

<section
  class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4"
  style="background-color: var(--color-rich-earth);"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Feature 2: Momentum Over Perfection -->
      <div
        class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(241,237,233,0.08)] hover:border-[rgba(0,208,156,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);"
      >
        <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" style="color: var(--color-jade);">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            class="w-full h-full"
          >
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 leading-snug"
          style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
        >
          Momentum Over Perfection
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          We track your trajectory, not just streaks. Miss a day? Get back up.
          We measure who you're becoming, not one bad day.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4: 8 Core Habits -->
      <div
        class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(241,237,233,0.08)] hover:border-[rgba(0,208,156,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);"
      >
        <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" style="color: var(--color-jade);">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            class="w-full h-full"
          >
            <polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"></polyline>
            <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 leading-snug"
          style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
        >
          8 Core Habits
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Workout, Meditation, Reading, Screen Time, Cold Showers, Running,
          Water, Wake-Up Time. The fundamentals that separate high performers
          from everyone else.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5: Your Potential Rating -->
      <div
        class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(241,237,233,0.08)] hover:border-[rgba(0,208,156,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);"
      >
        <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" style="color: var(--color-jade);">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            class="w-full h-full"
          >
            <path d="M3 3v18h18"></path>
            <path d="m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 leading-snug"
          style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
        >
          Your Potential Rating
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Live score showing the gap between current you and your ceiling. Every
          task completed closes that gap. Make it shrink daily.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6: 66-Day Psychology -->
      <div
        class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(241,237,233,0.08)] hover:border-[rgba(0,208,156,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);"
      >
        <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-6" style="color: var(--color-jade);">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            class="w-full h-full"
          >
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 leading-snug"
          style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
        >
          66-Day Psychology
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Research-proven timeframe for identity-level change. Not quick fixes.
          Real transformation that sticks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
